title: Arian Foster sustains Achilles tendon injury (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,530 Arian Foster sustains Achilles tendon injury (Yahoo Sports) Arian Foster went down in a heap without taking a hit. Foster injured his right Achilles tendon late in the fourth quarter of Houston's 44-26 loss at Miami on Sunday. Texans coach Bill O'Brien said he didn't know the severity of the injury, but added ''it obviously didn't look good.'' If Foster tore his Achilles, his season is over.
